　111 　年　　3 　　月　　18　　日\r\n　　　　　　　　　家事庭司法事務官","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PTDV/111%2c%e5%8f%b8%e7%b9%bc%2c346%2c20220318%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PTDV,111,司繼,346,20220318,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"司繼","JNO":"346","JDATE":"20220318","JTITLE":"拋棄繼承"}